					Do you really want to manually close this election? This cannot
					be undone.
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="modal-footer">
				<div class="w-100">
					<div class="row">
						<div class="col">
							<a
								href="#"
								class="btn btn-white w-100"
								data-bs-dismiss="modal"
							>
								Cancel
							</a>
						</div>
						<div class="col">
							<a href="#" class="btn btn-danger w-100"> Yes, Close </a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

